headline: Vickery Energy Acquires Appalachia Gas Assets from Tribune Resources
summary: FORT WORTH, Texas, Jan. 08, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Vickery Energy Partners, LLC (“Vickery”), a portfolio company of Quantum Capital Group, announced today that it has closed on the acquisition of Tribune Resources, LLC from Tribune Resources, Inc (“Tribune”). headline: Is EQT (EQT) Still Attractive After Recent Share Price Strength And DCF Reassessment
summary: If you are wondering whether EQT is still reasonably priced after its recent run, this article will walk through what the current share price could mean for potential value. EQT closed at US$54.49, with returns of 1.7% over the last week, a 7.1% decline over the last month, 1.9% year to date, 12.5% over 1 year, around 70.9% over 3 years and about 2.4x over 5 years. These figures may leave you questioning whether the stock is now stretched or still offers room for upside. Recent news around...
